title: Ep. 138 - The Blue Wave That Never Came
description:
Democrats promised a blue wave. What happened to it? We'll break down the election results. Also, I'll explain why Democrats taking the House might be the best thing that could have happened to President Trump. Finally, Florida voted to end the disenfranchisement of felons. It was the right call, I think, and I'll explain why. Date: 11-07-2018
